> seed.bitcoinstats.com			OK
> 
> testnet:
> 
> testnet-seed.bitcoin.petertodd.org	SERVFAIL, just from Telefonica
> testnet-seed.bluematt.me		OK (but only returns one node)
> 
> Note: Telefonica is one of Europe's largest ISPs.
